title: Five or Six foot tall ape looking creature observed picking up road kill.
observed: At 5 am Feb 9 1998  Heading north on 349 a small redish long haired ape looking creature about 5 foot five-6 foot tall, picking up road kill in the middle of the road ran off in to the woods
